%description
Provides sample size and power calculations when the treatment time-lag
effect is present and the lag duration is homogeneous across the
individual subject. The methods used are described in Xu, Z., Zhen, B.,
Park, Y., & Zhu, B. (2017) <doi:10.1002/sim.7157>.

